This portable class library provides Mersenne Twister PRNGs;

Mersenne Twister (MT):
- MT19937ar, MT19937ar-cok, MT19937ar-cok-opt
- MT19937-64, MT19937-64-opt

SIMD-oriented Fast MT (SFMT):
- SFMT-19937, SFMT-opt-19937

Double precision SFMT (dSFMT):
- dSFMT-19937, dSFMT-opt-19937
- dSFMT-opt-gen-* (Generics version for many Mersenne Exponents)
-- 521, 1279, 2203, 4253, 11213, 19937, 44497, 86243, 132049, 216091

You can use any PRNG via a corresponding System.Random derived wrapping class:
- MTRandom
- MT64Random
- SfmtRandom
- DsfmtRandom

and also we provide Randoms class for convenience that has;
- Randoms.Create method to get the suitable implementation such as fastest for Random.Next()
- Thread-local default object properties:
-- WellBalanced for general purpose
-- FastestInt32 for Random.Next()
-- FastestDouble for Random.Next(int) or Next(int,int) or NextDouble()

Further more, AccurateRandom class provides accurate results of Random.Next(int maxValue) and Next(int minValue, int maxValue).

ThymeTech DLL

All Classes below are thread safe

- Windows Validation (confirm that windows is legal and registered)
- Versioning of EXE's and DLL's 
- Twitter intergration (send / read messages)
- Thread Management (make controls - RichTextBox, TextBox, ProgressBar) thread safe
- Control over system date and time (ability to update / change / read the time and date)
- Convert Datatable -> CSV file (specify 3 parameters [DataTable, Separator for CSV eg: ",", and outputFileName)
- Convert CSV -> Datatable - similar to above
- Convert Dictionary -> CSV
- Convert CSV -> Dictionary
- Registration (GUI to register, Class to verify registration)
- Database utilities (MySQL, Pervasive, MsSQL) - like transaction handling (being, commit, rollback), connecting, etc...
- Logging class - link class to RichTextBox on form, all logging will go to richtextbox and be saved in log file with date stamp
- FTP Utilities - isValidConnection, Connect, GetFileList, DownloadFileAsText, DeleteFile, UploadFile
- Encryption Class (encrypt/decrypt our own registration and passwords, and Pastel Evolution passwords)
- Emailing class - Validate Address, SendGmail, SendEmail
- Configuration File (we use this to save settings etc.., its a standard windows ini file)
- Class that stores our common images / logos as byte array's and returns an object of type "Image"
- Zip / Unzip all files types (7zip, Rar, Zip, Gz, etc...) - view progress of unzip/zip also possible
- Website API's
 - City Power
 - Eskom
 - Eye Witness News
 - Google Maps
- Internet Explorer class - controls IE, allows you to open a IE window and send key's to items on the HTML based on their name / id and press buttons
- Microsoft Excel class - export datatable to excel, read excel sheet as datatable
- CSV File reading / writing - and handling advanced things like commas wrapped in double-quotes etc..

Client library to communication with Signere.no REST API.
		The library contains relevant model classes and a client class with methods to access all resources provided in the Signere.no API. 
		The client class itself is implemented from an interface to make it easily testable.
		
		All explicit communication with the API is handled internally and translated to POCO objects. 
		The client methods require certain fields from Signere.no user credentials in order to work properly. 
		To create a user account and obtain these credentials, please visit signere.no .  
		
		Also, check out the REST API documentation at Https://api.signere.no for further details about the resources that can be accessed through this library.

We provide conversion to all image formats supported by .NET framework via System.Drawing.Image class so you are able to export PDF files to BMP,JPG,PNG,TIFF as well as work with this bitmap on a fly.

We support rendering of the PDF content including:
- text (with embedded, externally linked, standard, simple and composite fonts)
- text search, bidi text search, highlighting, regions and coordinates extraction (including non-latin alphabets)
- images, including masked ones
- annotation objects of various types
- complex paths and fills
- PDF Forms
- all blending modes
- tiling patterns
- shading patterns of type 1,2,3(function-based, axial, radial)
- transparency groups(especially useful when you process files created with Adobe Illustrator)
- masked content(stencil masks, colorkey masks, softmasks)
- all colorspaces specified by PDF(in case of DeviceN we revert to alternative as specified by standard)
- PDF bookmarks + page navigation support
- compatible with Windows 10, WindowsRT and Windows Phone 8/10, so you may create Windows Store and Windows Phone Store apps that require PDF processing (see examples in our blog)
summary: Apitron PDF Rasterizer is a .NET component that performs quality conversion from PDF file to an image.
